@startuml ihsm_api_class
title IHsmApi Interface - Class Diagram

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam linetype ortho

interface "IHsmApi" as IHsmApi {
    +virtual ~IHsmApi() = 0
    
    ' Lifecycle
    +virtual Status init() = 0
    +virtual Status deinit() = 0
    +virtual bool isReady() const = 0
    
    ' Session Management
    +virtual Status createSession(SessionId& sessionId) = 0
    +virtual Status closeSession(SessionId sessionId) = 0
    +virtual bool isSessionValid(SessionId sessionId) const = 0
    
    ' Cryptographic Operations
    +virtual Status encrypt(SessionId sessionId, uint8_t keySlotId, 
                           Algorithm algorithm, 
                           span<const uint8_t> input,
                           span<uint8_t> output) = 0
    +virtual Status decrypt(SessionId sessionId, uint8_t keySlotId,
                           Algorithm algorithm,
                           span<const uint8_t> input,
                           span<uint8_t> output) = 0
    
    ' Key Management
    +virtual Status importKey(uint8_t keySlotId, Algorithm algorithm,
                             span<const uint8_t> keyData,
                             uint8_t permissions) = 0
    +virtual Status deleteKey(uint8_t keySlotId) = 0
    +virtual Status getKeySlotInfo(uint8_t keySlotId, 
                                   KeySlotInfo& info) = 0
    +virtual Status clearAllKeys() = 0
    
    ' Diagnostics
    +virtual const char* getVersion() const = 0
}

note right of IHsmApi
  **Purpose:** Public facade interface for HSM operations
  
  **Responsibilities:**
  - Unified API for all HSM functionality
  - Session-based operation
  - Key management
  - Cryptographic operations
  
  **Thread Safety:** Not thread-safe by default
  
  **Location:** include/ihsm_api.hpp
end note

IHsmApi ..> Status : returns
IHsmApi ..> SessionId : uses
IHsmApi ..> Algorithm : uses
IHsmApi ..> KeySlotInfo : uses

@enduml
